name: Rehearsals and Returns
blurb: This videogame is about conversations that will never take place.

rewards.reward:
The Game
=============================

Free download for PC or Mac.

Soundtrack\r\n=============================\r\nReceive the game and also the soundtrack by Sam Marshall, delivered as mp3 or flac download.  The soundtrack is likely to be available before the delivery date.

Wisdom Quote Contribution (Tier 5%)
=============================
Receive the game, the soundtrack, and also by late 2013 I will ask you to submit a "wisdom" quote.  Pick your favorite quote from history to be incorporated into the game's core mechanic.  (More under "Rewards and Rules", in the main page body, to the left)*.
This tier reward means there is about a 5% chance your quote will be available upon any one play-through, and you will get credit for this on the website.

Famous Figure Contribution (Tier 5%) ============================= Receive the game, the soundtrack, and also by late 2013 I will ask you to submit the name of a famous dead person. Pick your favorite famous dead figure to be in the released game. (More under "Rewards and Rules", in the main page body, to the left)**.  This tier reward means there is about a 5% chance your figure will be in any one play-through, and you will get credit for this on the website.

Wisdom Quote Contribution (Tier 10%) ============================= Receive the rewards from Pledge $25. But this tier reward means there is about a 10% chance your quote will be available upon any one play-through, and you will get credit for this on the website.

Famous Figure Contribution (Tier 10%) ============================= Receive the rewards from Pledge $40.   But this tier reward means there is about a 10% chance your figure will be in any one play-through, and you will get credit for this on the website.

Personal Screenshot Print ============================= Receive the rewards from Pledge $25, AND also an 8x10 print of an encounter of your choice - your avatar stating or quoting what you like, to the figure of your choice.  And you can pick your favorite setting (level) from the game.

Famous Figure Contribution (Tier 25%) ============================= Receive the rewards from Pledge $40 and the 8 x 10 in Pledge $80.  But this tier reward means there is about a 25% chance your figure will be in any one play-through, and you will get credit for this on the website.

Gift Version of the Game ============================= Receive the rewards from Pledge $25.  AND you will be asked to customize a version for a particular person.  In this giftable version, you will pick many of the things the avatar can say as well as all the figures that the player encounters.  This is intended as a unique gift for one or a few people.

Full Dedication ============================= Receive the rewards from Pledge $25.  Also a gift version of the game (Pledge $300), AND you can dedicate the game to someone in the closing credits.  (Recently born or recently passed people are recommended).
